{"tid":2234203,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"佛祖和耶穌，尚且要透過漫長歲月，風塵僕僕去宣揚其信念，甚至犧牲自己的性命，才能讓後世跟隨他們的步伐。","createTime":"2020-10-07T16:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T17:26:41.000Z","uid":184261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"364d6cb4b21596bfb85361da0dca369d3a019f3a","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"用一張工作紙就能夠攪港獨？厲害了，我的國！<br />\n<br />\n從前，在香港有一位老師，設計了一張工作紙。工作紙環繞著一個「官媒」節目的內容，讓學生了解甚麼是「言論自由」和「香港獨立」。完成功課後，普遍學生不認為「香港獨立」有足夠的條件，可是，設計這工作紙的老師，還是給教育局除牌，取消老師的資格，永不超生。<br />\n<br />\n理由是，這位老師「有計劃地散播港獨」。甚麼是散播？我的理解就是透過不同的媒介，向其他人展述自己的想法，而令到其他人明白或知道其意見。而這位老師，只不過是負責設計這工作紙，沒有參與課堂的學習，也沒有引導學生的想法和立場。他只是設計了一張題目為《不能逾越的紅線》的工作紙而已。"},{"pid":"11d3f5c0c9d43ac80b53cc871d2f11eb5cba8488","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>如果，這樣就能夠有計劃地散播港獨的話，我想，這位老師，定必是城府極深的小人。又或者，他是比佛祖和耶穌還要厲害的大大大人物。佛祖和耶穌，尚且要透過漫長歲月，風塵僕僕去宣揚其信念，甚至犧牲自己的性命，才能讓後世跟隨他們的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n可是這位老師，只不過用一張工作紙，沒頭沒尾幾個問題，就能夠為他人植入一顆「港獨」的種子。我想，如果給這位老師去做傳銷或賣保險，一定一定是「爆人爆數」到不得了的經典人物！</strong><br />\n<br />\n或許，我們都覺得這事情荒謬絕倫，甚至是天馬行空。可是，在沒有會面，沒有機會向教育局高層面前解釋的情况下，這位老師便被「釘牌」，終生不能教書，甚至步入任何學校。<br />\n<br />\n這件事情，讓市民萬分激動，這是如何的不合理啊！但是，在我的港，在我的國，這又是合理得不能再合理喎！冷靜下來，細心思量，在傳統學制下成長的我們，不都是習慣了在這個模式下長大嗎？<br />\n<br />\n做功課，測驗，考試，升班，做功課，測驗，考試，升班⋯⋯其實，從小到大，老師都沒有給我們任何機會去和他們表述我們學習的成果，甚至是關於個別課題的想法。老師和我們在學習上的溝通，就是做功課，測驗，考試，都是單向的。<br />\n<br />\n然後，老師看得舒服，和他思路一樣的，便會得高分，可以升班。老師看不明白，也不會找你來尋根究底，乾脆打幾個「交叉」就成了。至於閣下高深的創新想法，對不起，老師沒有時間，也沒有興趣知道。<br />\n<br />\n到近十年八載，大家越來越追求教績和成果，更直接把「低分但可能高能」放棄了。他們只會問家長，為甚麼你會讓孩子做錯？<br />\n<br />\n吓！？難道孩子在學校學習，就是為了每份功課都一模一樣？就是為了直接「撃中」Keywords 拿分數嗎？老師，那孩子不只是在抄你嗎？你真的想他抄你嗎？<br />\n<br />\n如此推算，其實教育局長是會計師，是量地師，甚至是禮儀師，對老師的評測也不會有差異。教育局需要的，只不過是倒模，只不過是人人都不過在抄你嘛，而沒有另類創新 Think out of the box 的想法。更莫論那些喜歡精益求精，正反論證，反覆討論的異常行為，這都是多餘又浪費時間的胡思亂想邪教行為而已。<br />\n<br />\n現在，在一張工作紙上，教育局看見：<br />\n<br />\n紅線，言論自由，香港獨立，觸動大陸，領土完整<br />\n<br />\n五大 Keywords，缺一不成，震撼了我的國，非要把這位老師捉出來祭旗不可！<br />\n<br />\n這位老師，能夠單憑以上五個生字就做到「有計劃地散播港獨」。我相信，也只有香港的「底氣」，才能夠「孕育」這個怪胎出來。<br />\n<br />\n厲害了，我的國！"},{"pid":"5627de2497157a466011d52785c43b6970d708e2","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://matters.news/@saanjaaiartisan/%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%99%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A0%E6%94%AA%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va?fbclid=IwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatters.news%2F%40saanjaaiartisan%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E6%2594%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%258E%25B2%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%258B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Bzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8d0e5e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://matters.news/@saanjaaiartisan/%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%99%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A0%E6%94%AA%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va?fbclid=IwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM</a>"},{"pid":"23faca4ff54d1315d0403050b96375e0d09b6030","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:47:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3d38201671ca4021cfc0bb3ec3552e1ea5c49b74","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"59cf10bc00a229d6df3c91efdd74affa44921516","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5e4f6558cc64a5dcc592e4689abbd65148321a2","tid":2234203,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"莫須有, 原來 真係有。"},{"pid":"b204a5d9bb3868c26bff73a9dfcbf67ddb0ca129","tid":2234203,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T17:26:41.000Z","msg":"希望阿sir 可以在其他平台為市民大眾做公民教育，例如YouTube，好多人都想聽聽阿sir講書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被釘牌不是終結，正苦比機會你走出課堂，轉型做大眾既老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油！"}],"pinned":{"pid":"5627de2497157a466011d52785c43b6970d708e2","tid":2234203,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://matters.news/@saanjaaiartisan/%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%99%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A0%E6%94%AA%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va?fbclid=IwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmatters.news%2F%40saanjaaiartisan%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%25B4%2599%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E6%2594%25AA%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E5%258E%25B2%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E4%25BA%2586-%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%259C%258B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM&d=xM4HlgsByf6UCiwKp%2FWW5Bzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8d0e5e1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://matters.news/@saanjaaiartisan/%E7%94%A8%E4%B8%80%E5%BC%B5%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E7%B4%99%E5%B0%B1%E8%83%BD%E5%A4%A0%E6%94%AA%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E5%8E%B2%E5%AE%B3%E4%BA%86-%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%8B-bafyreiaktodt2kwrpal5kqto5hlrdm67xy3horsfvrn7dsvffktm2nk5va?fbclid=IwAR0sL5KHbi70lj-PC9tKl3Z2wESJhk1rrpvqQLZxNLgHrmjCSz8BOs6NDDM</a>"}}